OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDespite
OL,6,Flargely clear skies many places will
OL,7,Fhave another warm or very warm night,
OL,8,Fespecially in large towns and cities
OL,9,Fwhere an exceptionally warm night is
OL,10,Fpossible. Remaining humid.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FSunny and generally very
OL,13,Fhot, locally exceptionally hot across
OL,14,Fwestern areas. The east or southeast
OL,15,Fbreeze will keep many coastal areas
OL,16,Fcooler than inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
